%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebulk%20packages%20may%20even%20cost%20more%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Also%2C%20buying%20in%20bulk%20can%20make%20the%20bill%20soar%20beyond%20what%20we%20should%20be%20spending%20that%20week%2C%20so%20if%20it%20isn't%20a%20really%20good%20deal%2C%20I%20opt%20for%20the%20practical%20pack%20in%20terms%20of%20both%20budget%20and%20our%20storage%20at%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22809a4875-b1cf-4c98-a6ad-fab4e7ba7c0d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20I%20know%20I'm%20saving%20money%2C%20I%20also%20feel%20OK%20buying%20occasional%20treats%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I'm%20saving%20money%20overall%2C%20I%20can%20afford%20a%20few%20treats%20or%20higher-priced%20items.%20My%20son%20and%20I%20really%20love%20salmon%2C%20but%20it's%20rarely%20on%20sale.%20It's%20too%20pricey%20to%20buy%20every%20week%2C%20but%20I%20try%20to%20get%20it%20at%20least%20once%20a%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20it%20isn't%20something%20we%20get%20to%20have%20regularly%2C%20my%20son%20and%20I%20appreciate%20it%20and%20enjoy%20it%20even%20more.%20There%20are%20also%20seasonal%20items%20that%20we%20love%2C%20like%20cherries%20or%20spaghetti%20squash%2C%20but%20since%20they're%20on%20the%20expensive%20end%2C%20I%20try%20to%20only%20buy%20them%20when%20they're%20in%20season%20and%20at%20a%20lower%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f520c8f-892b-43f9-af31-c585eca14b26%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20know%20which%20foods%20I%20can%20rely%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20grown%20to%20learn%20which%20foods%20are%20always%20affordable%2C%20nutritious%2C%20and%20enjoyable%20for%20my%20family.%20For%20example%2C%20bananas%20are%20always%20inexpensive%2C%20and%20they're%20good%20in%20so%20many%20ways%2C%20whether%20on%20the%20go%20as%20a%20snack%20with%20some%20peanut%20butter%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhealthy-smoothie-recipes-athletes-longevity-biohacker-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethrown%20into%20a%20smoothie%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20in%20our%20life%20when%20my%20budget%20was%20particularly%20tight%2C%20and%20we%20ate%20a%20lot%20of%20baby%20carrots%2C%20frozen%20peas%2C%20canned%20black%20beans%2C%20and%20apples.%20For%20meat%2C%20bone-in%20chicken%20drums%20and%20thighs%20are%20the%20least%20expensive%20kind%20and%20can%20be%20elevated%20when%20roasted%20in%20the%20oven%20with%20some%20seasoning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20I%20still%20focus%20on%20buying%20what%20I%20know%20my%20family%20will%20enjoy%20eating.%20If%20something%20is%20cheap%20but%20we%20don't%20love%20it%2C%20then%20to%20me%2C%20that's%20just%20a%20waste%20of%20money.%20From%20being%20forced%20to%20work%20within%20a%20tight%20budget%20for%20so%20long%20without%20wanting%20to%20sacrifice%20our%20health%20and%20pleasure%20around%20food%2C%20I%20still%20analyze%20which%20items%20we%20love%20that%20are%20most%20affordable%20and%20know%20when%20it's%20appropriate%20to%20spend%20a%20little%20more.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbudget-grocery-shopping-single-mom-meal-planning-sales-treats-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720518123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668c2751098114dafd1a5f0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbudget-grocery-shopping-single-mom-meal-planning-sales-treats-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20I%20was%20a%20single%20mom%20I%20learned%20how%20to%20grocery%20shop%20on%20a%20tight%20budget%20while%20still%20buying%20healthy%20food.%20I%20meal-plan%2C%20compare%20prices%2C%20and%20watch%20sales.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ashley%20Archambault)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbudget-grocery-shopping-single-mom-meal-planning-sales-treats-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lawyer%20Complains%20To%20Chief%20Justice%20About%20Fellow%20Judge.%20His%20Response%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20witnessed%20dramatic%20exchanges%20when%20a%20Lucknow-based%20advocate%20requested%20two%20separate%20benches%20to%20pardon%20him%20and%20remove%20costs%20imposed%20on%20him%20for%20filing%20frivolous%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Justice%20Augustine%20G%20Masih%20pulled%20up%20Lucknow-based%20advocate%20Ashok%20Pandey%20for%20not%20paying%20cost%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%20imposed%20on%20him.%20The%20cost%20was%20imposed%20last%20year%20after%20the%20top%20court%20dismissed%20the%20lawyer's%20plea%20challenging%20the%20appointment%20of%20Supreme%20Court%20advocates%20as%20High%20Court%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20lawyer%20travelled%20abroad%20soon%20after%20the%20court%20imposed%20the%20cost.%20%26quot%3BNow%20you%20cannot%20say%20that%20you%20can't%20pay%20cost%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20he%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpractising%20lawyer%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20Mr%20Pandey%20said%20he%20has%20not%20got%20a%20single%20case%20since%20last%20year%20and%20that%20his%20trip%20was%20%26quot%3Bsponsored%20by%20my%20kids%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20pay%20the%20cost%20in%20a%20week%20else%20we%20will%20issue%20a%20contempt%20(notice).%20Are%20you%20willing%20to%20pay%20in%202%20weeks%20or%20not%3F%20You%20are%20the%20member%20of%20the%20bar%2C%20we%20request%20you%20to%20answer%20it%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20replied%20that%20his%20%26quot%3Bchildren%20are%20rich%2C%20but%20I%20am%20poor%26quot%3B.%20Referring%20to%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20Dipak%20Misra%2C%20he%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20initially%20filed%20several%20petitions%20for%20CJI%20Dipak%20Misra%20when%20a%20lot%20of%20allegations%20were%20put%20against%20him.%20Nobody%20from%20this%20court%20supported%20him%20but%20I%20was%20there.%20I%20have%20requested%20the%20CJI%20and%20President%20of%20India%20for%20the%20payment%20in%20those%20cases.%20CJI%20has%20referred%20my%20matter%20to%20SCLSC%20(Supreme%20Court%20Legal%20Services%20Committee)%20for%20payment.%20I%20will%20pay%20lordship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%20granted%20the%20lawyer%20time%20till%20August%205%20and%20added%20that%20the%20court%20will%20issue%20a%20contempt%20notice%20if%20the%20payment%20is%20not%20made%20by%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20was%20then%20puilled%20up%20by%20another%20bench%20--%20of%20Justice%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20Justice%20KV%20Viswanathan%20--%20for%20not%20paying%20Rs%201%20Lakh%20imposed%20on%20him%20in%20a%20separate%20matter.%20This%20was%20in%20connection%20to%20a%20PIL%20last%20year%20in%20which%20Mr%20Pandey%20had%20challenged%20the%20reinstatement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Membership%20of%20NCP's%20Mohd%20Faizal%20Padippura.%20The%20court%20had%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20lawyer%20over%20the%20frivolous%20PIL.%20Mr%20Pandey%20has%20earlier%20also%20challenged%20the%20oath%20taken%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Bombay%20High%20Court.%20He%20had%20said%20that%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20did%20not%20say%20%26quot%3BI%26quot%3B%20while%20taking%20the%20oath.%20This%20lawyer%20had%20also%20challenged%20the%20restoration%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Lok%20Sabha%20membership%2C%20attracting%20another%20fine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gavai%20asked%20the%20lawyer%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20courts%20have%20imposed%20cost%20on%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20He%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BPlease%20recall%20the%20cost.%20I%20don't%20have%20money.%26quot%3B%20The%20bench%20rejected%20the%20plea%2C%20but%20the%20lawyer%20persisted.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20leave%20the%20court%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20embarrass%20ourselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Gavai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20stayed%20put%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20requesting%20with%20folded%20hands.%20This%20is%20no%20contempt%2C%20Sir...%20Please%20remove%20cost%20from%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%C2%A0He%20then%20addressed%20Justice%20Gavai%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20also%20going%20to%20be%20next%20CJI.%26quot%3B%20The%20judge%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BGod%20knows%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20leaving%20or%20not%3F%20We%20have%20to%20call%20the%20security%20personnel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Gavai%20is%20the%20third%20seniormost%20judge%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20is%20in%20line%20to%20be%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20not%20all.%20Mr%20Pandey%20then%20approached%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20complained%20against%20Justice%20Gavai.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20senior%20judge%20had%20warned%20him%20that%20his%20%26quot%3Bsanad%26quot%3B%20--%20meaning%20licence%20to%20practice%20law%20--%20will%20be%20revoked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%20that%20heated%20arguments%20do%20take%20place%2C%20but%20warned%20the%20lawyer%20against%20making%20such%20allegations.%20%26quot%3BYou%20cannot%20make%20allegations%20like%20this%20on%20the%20judges%20of%20the%20bench.%20They%20never%20misbehave%20with%20lawyers.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20challenge%20the%20fines%2C%20file%20a%20review%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20pulled%20up%20petitioners%20and%20lawyers%20over%20frivolous%20PILs%2C%20with%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20saying%20that%20the%20public%20is%20paying%20for%20precious%20judicial%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720518120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fcqdr7rto_cji-justice-gavai_625x300_09_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-justice-br-gavai-frivolous-pil-lawyer-complains-to-chief-justice-about-fellow-judge-his-response-6066784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20witnessed%20dramatic%20exchanges%20when%20a%20Lucknow-based%20advocate%20requested%20two%20separate%20benches%20to%20pardon%20him%20and%20remove%20costs%20imposed%20on%20him%20for%20filing%20frivolous%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-justice-br-gavai-frivolous-pil-lawyer-complains-to-chief-justice-about-fellow-judge-his-response-6066784%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-justice-br-gavai-frivolous-pil-lawyer-complains-to-chief-justice-about-fellow-judge-his-response-6066784%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-justice-br-gavai-frivolous-pil-lawyer-complains-to-chief-justice-about-fellow-judge-his-response-6066784%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Europe's%20company%20CEO%20on%20why%20stopping%20Chinese%20chips%20makes%20'no%20point'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720518063000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111604203%2Cimgsize-75414.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fceo-of-europes-largest-chip-company-on-why-stopping-legacy-chinese-chips-makes-no-point%2Farticleshow%2F111604237.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22European%20car%20companies%20face%20challenges%20in%20sourcing%20older%20generation%20computer%20chips%2C%20with%20ASML%20CEO%20highlighting%20Europe's%20dependency%20on%20China.%20Despite%20global%20demand%20rising%2C%20Europe%20falls%20short%20in%20meeting%20its%20own%20chip%20needs.%20China's%20chip%20production%20capacity%20is%20projected%20to%20outpace%20the%20global%20rate%20by%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fceo-of-europes-largest-chip-company-on-why-stopping-legacy-chinese-chips-makes-no-point%2Farticleshow%2F111604237.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explainer%3A%20Why%20Democrats%20Are%20Urging%20Biden%20To%20Step%20Out%20Of%20Presidential%20Race%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFifty-six%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20US%20President%20appeared%20on%20television%20and%20announced%2C%20to%20the%20nation's%20shock%2C%20that%20he'd%20not%20seek%20re-election.%20His%20name%20was%20Lyndon%20B.%20Johnson%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20US%20President%20to%20not%20run%20for%20his%20second%20elected%20term.%20The%20reasons%20were%20many%20and%20varied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%201963%2C%20Johnson%2C%20the%20then%20US%20Vice-President%2C%20ascended%20to%20the%20top%20job%20following%20the%20assassination%20of%20then-President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20he%20registered%20a%20landslide%20victory%20for%20Democrats%20in%20Presidential%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20changed%20after%20he%20presided%20over%20the%20deeply%20unpopular%20Vietnam%20War.%20Even%20though%20he%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20Democratic%20nominee%20in%201968%2C%20his%20health%2C%20plunging%20approval%20ratings%20and%20the%20way%20he%20handled%20the%20war%20--%20all%20went%20against%20him.%20Johnson%20decided%20it%20was%20time%20for%20him%20to%20make%20way%20for%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast-forward%20to%202024%2C%20another%20US%20President's%20reelection%20bid%20is%20in%20jeopardy.%20This%20time%2C%20it's%20Joe%20Biden%20faced%20with%20growing%20calls%20from%20within%20the%20party%20to%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20presidential%20race.%20Citing%20concerns%20about%20his%20health%20and%20ability%20to%20take%20on%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20prominent%20House%20Democrats%20have%20doubted%20Biden's%20fitness%20for%20office%20and%20his%20chances%20of%20winning%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20mounting%20pressure%2C%20Biden%20remains%20defiant%2C%20insisting%20he%20will%20stay%20in%20the%20race.%20But%20will%20his%20determination%20be%20enough%20to%20overcome%20the%20rising%20dissent%20against%20his%20candidacy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20a%20group%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024-election%2Ffour-democrats-congress-call-biden-step-2024-race-rcna160625%5C%22%3EDemocratic%20lawmakers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Reps%20Adam%20Smith%2C%20Jerry%20Nadler%2C%20Mark%20Takano%20and%20Joe%20Morelle%2C%20gathered%20to%20discuss%20their%20party's%20future.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20they%20all%20agreed%20that%20President%20Biden%20should%20withdraw%20from%20the%20presidential%20race.%20This%20was%20also%20echoed%20publicly%20by%20Rep%20Adam%20Smith%20in%20a%20Monday%20interview%20with%20CNN%2C%20where%20he%20openly%20called%20for%20Biden%20to%20drop%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERep%20Angie%20Craig%20urged%20President%20Biden%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fbrianbushard%2F2024%2F07%2F05%2Fbiden-calls-debate-just-a-bad-episode-i-was-sick-in-abc-interview%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3Ewithdraw%20from%20the%20presidential%20race%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20his%20interview%20with%20ABC%20News'%20George%20Stephanopoulos.%20Craig%20cited%20Biden's%20disappointing%20debate%20performance%20and%20his%20inability%20to%20deliver%20a%20strong%20response%20in%20the%20aftermath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReps%20Mike%20Quigley%20and%20Seth%20Moulton%20have%20joined%20the%20growing%20chorus%20of%20Democrats%20calling%20for%20President%20Biden%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20presidential%20race.%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.msnbc.com%2Fall-in%2Fwatch%2Fdem-rep-mike-quigley-calls-on-biden-to-step-aside-let-someone-else-do-this-214313029546%C2%A0%5C%22%3EMSNBC%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Chris%20Hayes%2C%20Quigley%20said%20that%20stepping%20down%20is%20the%20only%20way%20for%20Biden%20to%20secure%20his%20legacy%20and%20prevent%20a%20disastrous%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Seth%20Moulton%20said%20he%20didn't%20have%20confidence%20in%20Biden's%20ability%20to%20defeat%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20November%2C%20urging%20him%20to%20%26quot%3Bstep%20aside%20and%20let%20new%20leaders%20rise%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Boston's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.wbur.org%2Fnews%2F2024%2F07%2F04%2Fmoulton-says-biden-drop-out-election%C2%A0%5C%22%3EWBUR%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReps%20Lloyd%20Doggett%20and%20Raul%20Grijalva%20were%20among%20the%20first%20sitting%20Democrats%20to%20urge%20President%20Biden%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20race.%20Doggett%20said%20he%20was%20disappointed%20that%20Biden%20failed%20to%20defend%20his%20accomplishments%20and%20expose%20Trump's%20lies%20during%20the%20debate%2C%20while%20Grijalva%20said%20it%20was%20Biden's%20%26quot%3Bresponsibility%26quot%3B%20to%20step%20down.%20Former%20Secretary%20of%20Housing%20and%20Urban%20Development%20Julian%20Castro%20also%20joined%20the%20calls%20for%20Biden%20to%20withdraw%2C%20suggesting%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%20as%20a%20suitable%20replacement%20on%20the%20Democratic%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden's%20performance%20in%20the%20first%20debate%20was%20widely%20criticised%2C%20with%20many%20saying%20he%20appeared%20weak%20and%20disoriented.%20He%20struggled%20to%20speak%20clearly%2C%20fumbled%2C%20gave%20confusing%