%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20offer%20came%20calling%2C%20Gambhir%20found%20it%20tough%20to%20resist%20the%20temptation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gambhir's%20impending%20departure%20to%20the%20Indian%20team%20would%20leave%20a%20big%20void%20at%20KKR%2C%20considering%20the%20franchise%20hugely%20benefitted%20from%20his%20guidance%2C%20clinching%20the%20IPL%202024%20title.%20The%20franchise's%20bosses%20have%20reportedly%20put%20Dravid's%20name%20on%20the%20top%20of%20their%20shortlist%20for%20the%20role%20that%20Gambhir%20will%20be%20leaving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbengali.news18.com%2Fphotogallery%2Fsports%2Fas-per-sources-kolkata-knight-riders-contact-rahul-dravid-to-take-charge-of-kkr-in-ipl-2024-offer-huge-money-sup-1744912.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENews%2018%20Bangla%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20number%20of%20IPL%20franchises%20are%20keen%20to%20hire%20Dravid%20as%20coach%20or%20mentor%20ahead%20of%20the%202025%20season.%20The%20Knight%20Riders%20also%20have%20him%20on%20the%20radar%2C%20though%20no%20concrete%20discussion%20has%20taken%20place%20as%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20lifted%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20title%2C%20beating%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20final%2C%20Dravid%20did%20joke%20about%20being%20'jobless'%20from%20the%20next%20month%2C%20and%20was%20asking%20reporters%20if%20they%20have%20any%20offers.%20A%20man%20of%20the%20talent%20of%20Dravid%2C%20and%20the%20gold-worthy%20experience%20in%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20franchises%20are%20understandably%20lining%20up%20to%20rope%20him%20into%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid%20didn't%20want%20to%20continue%20as%20the%20Indian%20team's%20head%20coach%20as%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%2010%20months%20a%20year%20travelling%2C%20keeping%20himself%20away%20from%20the%20family.%20But%2C%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20is%20different.%20In%20the%20T20%20league%2C%20Dravid%20only%20needs%20to%20be%20with%20the%20franchise%20for%202-3%20months%20a%20year%2C%20a%20prospect%20he%20could%20fancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20India%20captain%20has%20worked%20as%20a%20mentor%20and%20coach%20with%20IPL%20franchises%20in%20the%20past.%20Dravid%20was%20the%20coach%20of%20Delhi%20Daredevils%20franchise%20before%20leaving%20the%20job%20in%202017%20over%20'conflict%20of%20interest'.%20Since%20ending%20his%20IPL%20career%2C%20Dravid%20has%20worked%20as%20the%20coach%20of%20India's%20junior%20teams%2C%20including%20Under-19%20and%20India%20A.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20most%20recently%20working%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20in%20Bengaluru%20before%20taking%20up%20the%20India%20job%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720516140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fvo37trl8_rahul-dravid-_625x300_29_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Frahul-dravid-approached-to-replace-gautam-gambhir-at-kkr-report-6066589%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20straight%20swap%20between%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20Rahul%20Dravid%20is%20possible%2C%20with%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20reportedly%20eyeing%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup-winning%20India%20coach%20as%20their%20new%20mentor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Frahul-dravid-approached-to-replace-gautam-gambhir-at-kkr-report-6066589%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Frahul-dravid-approached-to-replace-gautam-gambhir-at-kkr-report-6066589%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Frahul-dravid-approached-to-replace-gautam-gambhir-at-kkr-report-6066589%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2272%20Hours%20After%20BMW%20Hit-And-Run%2C%20Mihir%20Shah%20Still%20Missing%2C%20Family%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThree%20days