%20India's%20victory%20in%20the%20Men's%20T20%20cricket%20world%20cup%20that%20ended%20the%2013-year%20ICC%20trophy%20drought%20for%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%202014%2C%20we%20were%20into%20the%20pit%20of%20despair.%20Today%2C%20the%20country%20is%20full%20of%20confidence.%20Two%20patients%20suffering%20from%20the%20same%20ailment%20are%20in%20the%20same%20hospital%2C%20similarly%20capable%20doctors%20are%20attending%20to%20them.%20But%20if%20one%20patient%20is%20hopeful%20and%20the%20other%20is%20in%20despair%2C%20you%20will%20see%20the%20hopeful%20one%20will%20recover%20soon.%20India's%20asset%20now%20is%20its%20confidence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20must%20have%20celebrated%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20victory%20here.%20The%20real%20story%20of%20that%20win%20is%20the%20journey%20towards%20it.%20Today's%20young%20India%20does%20not%20accept%20defeat%20till%20the%20last%20ball%20and%20the%20last%20moment.%20And%20victory%20kisses%20the%20feet%20of%20those%20who%20do%20not%20accept%20defeat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShowcasing%20his%20government's%20achievements%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20India%20hosts%20the%20G20%20Summit%20at%20the%20scale%20at%20which%20it%20did%2C%20the%20world%20takes%20notice.%20When%20India%20electrifies%2040%2C000%20km%20of%20rail%20lines%2C%20then%20the%20world%20notices%20India's%20power%20to%20grow.%20When%20India%20launches%20a%20solar%20mission%20and%20successfully%20and%20takes%20an%20L1%20orbit%2C%20when%20India%20lands%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20when%20India%20builds%20the%20world's%20highest%20rail%20bridge%2C%20when%20India%20build's%20the%20world's%20tallest%20statue%2C%20the%20world%20sees%20a%20growing%20India.%20And%20India%20can%20do%20all%20this%20because%20of%20the%20potential%20and%20capability%20of%20140%20crore%20Indians%2C%20of%20its%20talented%20diaspora%20in%20every%20country%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20India%20and%20Russia%20are%20working%20together%20to%20boost%20global%20prosperity.%20%26quot%3BYou%20all%20are%20taking%20India-Russia%20ties%20to%20new%20heights.%20With%20your%20hard%20work%20and%20honesty%2C%20you%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20Russian%20society.%20I%20have%20been%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20unique%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Russia%20as%20India's%20%26quot%3Ball-weather%20ally%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btrustworthy%20friend%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20relationship%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20based%20on%20mutual%20trust%20and%20respect.%20%26quot%3BOur%20ties%20have%20been%20tested%20multiple%20times%2C%20and%20our%20friendship%20has%20always%20emerged%20strong.%20I%20thank%20my%20friend%2C%20President%20Putin%20for%20his%20leadership.%20For%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20he%20has%20worked%20to%20make%20this%20partnership%20stronger.%20This%20is%20my%206th%20visit%20to%20Russia%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20and%20we%20have%20met%20each%20other%2017%20times%20during%20this%20time.%20These%20meetings%20have%20strengthened%20trust%20and%20respect.%20When%20our%20students%20were%20stuck%20amid%20(Ukraine)%20conflict%2C%20President%20Putin%20helped%20us%20take%20them%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20it%20is%20his%20honour%20that%20his%20first%20diaspora%20event%20after%20being%20elected%20for%20the%20third%20time%20is%20happening%20in%20Moscow.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20taken%20a%20pledge%20that%20I%20will%20work%20thrice%20as%20hard%20and%20thrice%20as%20fast%20as%20I%20have%20in%20the%20first%20two%20terms.%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20that%20in%20this%20third%20term%2C%20you%20will%20see%20that%20India%20will%20challenge%20every%20challenge%20that%20comes%20its%20way.%20And%20it%20is%20in%20my%20DNA%20that%20I%20give%20chunauti%20(challenge)%20to%20e