interview%20with%20Dax%20Shepard%20on%20his%20podcast%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farmchairexpertpod.com%2Fpods%2Fmeghan-trainor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArmchair%20Expert%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BMade%20You%20Look%26quot%3B%20singer%20shared%20her%20potty%20training%20method%20while%20discussing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2Fsitz-bath%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanal%20fissures%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20potty%20training%20my%20kid%2C%20so%20don't%20attack%20me%20internet%2C%20but%20I%20pooped%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Trainor%2C%2030%2C%20told%20Shepard.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20on%20his%20little%20potty%2C%20and%20I%20was%20over%20here.%20I%20know%20I%20can%20smell%20my%20poop%2C%20but%20we%20were%20like%2C%20'We%20did%20it%2C%20buddy!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Trainor%20has%20brought%20up%20toilet%20talk.%20In%202021%2C%20she%20was%20interviewed%20with%20her%20brother%20Ryan%20Trainor%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-trainor-shares-new-relationship-story-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20Won't%20You%20Date%20Me%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast%20hosted%20by%20Nicole%20Byer.%20%26quot%3BThey%20poop%20together.%20She's%20pooping%20and%20Daryl's%20like%2C%20'I'm%20going%20to%20go%20hang%20out%20with%20you%20now!'%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20said%20about%20his%20sister%20and%20her%20husband%20on%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrainor%20told%20Byer%20that%20she%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20actor%20Daryl%20Sabara%2C%20had%20installed%20two%20toilet%20bowls%20side%20by%20side%20in%20their%20house.%20The%20setup%20has%20also%20helped%20ease%20nighttime%20parenting%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20we%20have%20young%20babies%2C%20so%20we're%20getting%20up%20every%20hour%20on%20the%20hour%2C%20and%20this%20dude%20pees%20like%20a%20girl.%20So%20I%20was%20like%2C%20get%20out%20of%20my%20way%2C%20I%20have%20to%20piss%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Shepard.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20solved%20this%20crime%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20we're%20gonna%20pee%20at%20the%20same%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20clarified%2C%20however%2C%20that%20their%20shared%20bathroom%20time%20was%20limited%20to%20peeing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrainor%20and%20Sabara%20married%20in%20December%202018%20after%20dating%20for%20almost%20two%20years.%20They%20welcomed%20their%20son%2C%20Riley%2C%20in%20February%202021%20and%20their%20second%20son%2C%20Barry%20Bruce%2C%20in%20July%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Trainor%20has%20been%20open%20about%20motherhood%20and%20parenting%2C%20including%20developing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeghan-trainor-had-ptsd-traumatic-birth-of-her-son-report-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost-traumatic%20stress%20disorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20complicated%20birth%20of%20her%20first%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrainor%20is%20not%20the%20only%20celebrity%20sharing%20her%20potty%20training%20methods.%20In%202020%2C%20actor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkristen-bell-daughter-diapers-potty-training-2020-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKristen%20Bell%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20her%20podcast%20%26quot%3BMomsplaining%20with%20Kristen%20Bell%26quot%3B%20that%20when%20her%20older%20daughter%20was%2021%20months%2C%20she%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Dax%20Shepard%2C%20had%20simply%20suggested%20she%20use%20the%20toilet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20lying%20in%20bed%20giggling%20about%20this%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%2C%20like%2C%20'Why%20does%20everyone%20make%20a%20big%20deal%20out%20of%20this%20potty%20training%3F%20It's%20so%20easy.%20Just%20tell%20the%20kid%20to%20use%20the%20toilet%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20explain%20that%20it%20wasn't%20as%20