little%20miffed%20around%20here%20about%20how%20information%20has%20been%20shared%20with%20the%20press%20corps%20by%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20reporter%20asked%20White%20House%20Press%20Secretary%20Karine%20Jean-Pierre%20during%20her%20daily%20news%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20visitors'%20log%20suggests%20that%20Parkinson's%20specialist%20Dr%20Kevin%20Cannard%20visited%20the%20building%20eight%20times%20in%20eight%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reporters%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20seen%20by%20the%20Parkinson's%20specialist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20matter%20how%20hard%20you%20push%20me%2C%20it%20does%20not%20matter%20how%20angry%20you%20get%20with%20me%2C%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20confirm%20a%20name.%20It%20does%20not%20matter%20if%20it%20is%20even%20in%20the%20log.%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that%20from%20here.%20What%20I%20can%20share%20with%20you%20is%20that%20the%20president%20has%20seen%20a%20neurologist%20for%20his%20physical%20three%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Jean-Pierre%20told%20the%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20more%20than%20what%20the%20last%20guy%20shared%20and%20it%20is%20in%20line%20with%20what%20George%20W%20Bush%20did.%20It%20is%20in%20line%20with%20what%20(Barack)%20Obama%20did.%20And%20so%20it%20is%20comprehensive.%20It%20is%20out%20there....%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20going%20to%20devolve%20somebody's%20name%20or%20confirm%20someone.%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that.%20That%20is%20--%20as%20a%20privacy%20for%20that%20person.%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that.%20It%20does%20not%20matter%20how%20hard%20you%20push%20me.%20It%20does%20not%20matter%20how%20angry%20you%20get%20with%20me%20from%20here.%20I%20am%20just%20not%20going%20to%20do%20that.%20It%20is%20inappropriate%20and%20it%20is%20not%20acceptable%2C%20so%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Jean-Pierre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EB