s%20generation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktan%40businessinsider.com%20(Kwan%20Wei%20Kevin%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A111%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-makeover-reason-email-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20In%20God's%20Name%3A%20How%20'Babas'%20And%20'Matas'%20Feed%20On%20Insecurity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fmq5ee298_bhole-baba_625x300_09_July_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20a%20tragic%20stampede%20in%20Hathras%20on%20July%202%20that%20claimed%20121%20lives%2C%20self-styled%20godman%20Suraj%20Pal%20Singh%2C%20a.k.a.%20'Bhole%20Baba'%2C%20has%20still%20not%20been%20arrested.%20In%20fact%2C%20through%20his%20lawyer%2C%20Singh%20continues%20to%20hurl%20new%20allegations%20about%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20stampede.%20The%20Hathras%20tragedy%20yet%20again%20brings%20to%20the%20fore%20Indians'%20unhealthy%20obsession%20with%20%3Cem%3Ebabas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Ematas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20despite%20the%20plethora%20of%20controversies%20and%20criminal%20cases%20that%20frequently%20come%20up%20against%20such%20god-men%20and%20-women.%20People%20from%20even%20the%20most%20disadvantaged%20backgrounds%20don't%20mind%20waiting%20for%20hours%20for%20'darshan'%20and%20spending%20their%20last%20saved%20penny%20as%20'%3Cem%3Edakshina%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebaba's%3C%2Fem%3E%20'magical%20powers'%20would%20cure%20their%20sickness%20and%20eradicate%20their%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurus%20have%20been%20part%20of%20Indian%20tradition%20for%20ages%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20many%20of%20them%20brought%20succour%20to%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20followers%20in%20the%20form%20of%20moral%20guidance%20and%20financial%20help.%20Many%20have%20also%20worked%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20lower%20castes%2C%20who%20have%20long%20been%20discriminated%20against%20in%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20modern%20Indian%20godmen%2C%20however%2C%20are%20a%20different%20brand.%20They%20are%20flashy%2C%20powerful%2C%20influential%2C%20more%20connected%20to%20the%20worldly%20world%2C%20and%20draw%20huge%20crowds%20of%20supporters.%20And%2C%20they%20are%20not%20new%20to%20scandals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGodmen%20And%20Crime%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodmen%20like%20Gurmeet%20Ram%20Rahim%20Singh%20and%20Asaram%20Bapu%20have%20in%20the%20past%20faced%20charges%20for%20crimes%20like%20murder%2C%20rape%2C%20tax%20evasion%20and%20fraud.%20But%20Indians%20continue%20to%20be%20in%20thrall%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20misdeeds%20and%20corruption%20of%20one%20such%20godman%2C%20Nithyananda%2C%20came%20to%20light%20after%20a%20video%20of%20him%20engaging%20in%20sleazy%20acts%20with%20women%20surfaced%20in%20the%20media.%20He%20fled%20India%20and%20has%20remained%20in%20hiding%20since%202019.%20In%20December%20of%20that%20year%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20he%20had%20created%20a%20new%20Hindu%20micronation%2C%20'Kailaasa'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20India%2C%20we%20see%20godmen%20as%20someone%20who%20would%20give%20us%20instant%20relief%20from%20anxiety%20and%20pain.%20Poverty%20and%20unemployment%20contribute%20to%20such%20anxieties%20and%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20babas%20whose%20'social%20healing'%20comforts%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Malinee%20Priya%2C%20Associate%20Professor%20of%20Psychology%20at%20Dr%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhole%20Baba's%20Adventures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20case%2C%20what's%20surprising%20is%20that%20few%20had%20heard%20about%20Bhole%20Baba%20before%20the%20stampede%20made%20national%20headlines.%20There%20are%20many%20other%20such%20religious%20'gurus'%20operating%20across%20India.%20Reportedly%2C%20for%2018%20years%2C%20Bhole%20Baba%20had%20been%20a%20constable%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%2C%20working%20across%20various%20districts%20and%20spending%20time%20with%20the%20intelligence%20unit.%20Perhaps%20it%20was%20this%20experience%20that%20gave%20him%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20societal%20dynamics%20and%20human%20psychology%2C%20which%20he%20later%20capitalised%20on%20to%20build%20his%20following.%20Singh%20had%20already%20been%20embroiled%20in%20several%20legal%20cases%20-%20including%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault%20-%20but%20that%20didn't%20deter%20his%20supporters%2C%20who%20continued%20to%20see%20him%20as%20a%20'healer'%20and%20'exorcist'.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20for%20taking%20a%20dead%20girl%20away%20from%20her%20family%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20could%20resurrect%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Miracles'%20And%20Religion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20often%20people%20from%20disadvantaged%20or%20marginalised%20backgrounds%2C%20ignored%20by%20the%20state%20and%20society%20and%20left%20to%20face%20their%20own%20hardships%2C%20who%20turn%20to%20gurus%20for%20'spiritual%20and%20material%20sustenance'.%20Dr%20Shivani%20Katara%2C%20a%20PhD%20in%20Social%20Medicine%20from%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20says%20for%20most%20Indians%2C%20'miracle'%20is%20just%20another%20word%20for%20religion.%20%26quot%3BMiracles%20establish%20a%20saint's%20'saintliness'%20among%20masses.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20'miracles'%20raise%20the%20general%20religious%20consciousness%20of%20the%20people.%20People%20often%20flock%20to%20godmen%20to%20alleviate%20their%20miseries%20when%20they%20think%20that%20society%2C%20conventional%20religion%20and%20politics%20have%20failed%20them%20...%20Despite%20cases%20of%20people%20getting%20duped%20or%20physically%20harmed%2C%20many%20continue%20to%20put%20full%20faith%20in%20unconventional%20cults%20like%20'Dera%20Sacha%20Sauda'%20or%20leaders%20like%20'Bhole%20Baba'%2C%20as%20these%20godmen%20provide%20them%20with%20hope%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20security.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20political%20connections%20backing%20these%20godmen%20are%20also%20a%20factor.%20When%20common%20people%20see%20politicians%20and%20celebrities%20visiting%20them%2C%20they're%20impressed%2C%20only%20adding%20to%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20baba.%20Take%20the%20case%20of%20Singh.%20His%20political%20connections%20grew%20in%202007%20under%20Mayawati's%20rule%3B%20public%20appearances%20with%20prominent%20leaders%20amplified%20his%20influence.%20His%20followers%20constituted%20a%20crucial%20vote%20bank%2C%20and%20his%20ashrams%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20symbolised%20his%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20powerful%20often%20patronise%20godmen%20to%20justify%20their%20accumulation%20of%20wealth%20and%20to%20encash%20on%20Baba's%20popularity%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Priya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20vicious%20circle%2C%20indeed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20Contributing%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720509660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fso4l1ru_bhole-baba_625x300_09_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-gods-name-how-indias-godmen-babas-and-matas-feed-on-insecurity-6066005%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20modern%20Indian%20godmen%20are%20a%20different%20brand.%20They%20are%20flashy%2C%20powerful%2C%20influential%2C%20more%20connected%20to%20the%20worldly%20world%2C%20and%2