0and%20can't%20make.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanva's%20AI%20feature%2C%20called%20Magic%20Media%2C%20doesn't%20work%20with%20medical%20or%20political%20terms%2C%20because%20such%20content%20may%20be%20harmful%20or%20inappropriate%2C%20CEO%20Melanie%20Perkins%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24191080%2Fcanva-ceo-melanie-perkins-design-ai-adobe-competition-decoder-podcast-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20The%20Verge%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Monday.%20Canva's%20software%20can%20be%20used%20to%20create%20anything%20from%20party%20invitations%20to%20social%20media%20content%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanva-templates-how-to-make-millions-selling-digital-products-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresentation%20templates%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCanva%20has%20been%20designed%20to%20be%20a%20platform%20where%20you%20can%20come%20in%20and%20take%20your%20idea%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20design%2C%20but%20there%20are%20certain%20things%20we%20shouldn't%20be%20generating%2C%26quot%3B%20Perkins%2C%20who%20cofounded%20the%2011-year-old%20company%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Perkins%20said%20that%20if%20the%20tool%20is%20prompted%20to%20create%20images%20of%20political%20candidates%2C%20it%20will%20simply%20tell%20the%20user%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20can%20still%20create%20designs%20with%20political%20or%20health%20content%20on%20the%20platform%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanva%20also%20does%20not%20allow%20AI%20to%20be%20used%20for%20generating%20contracts%2C%20legal%20or%20financial%20advice%2C%20spam%2C%20or%20adult%20content%2C%20according%20to%20its%20AI%20product%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20has%20a%20clear%20policy%20on%20AI%20scraping.%20Canva%20does%20not%20train%20its%20AI%20on%20creators'%20content%20without%20permission%2C%20and%20users%20can%20