0World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-kash-patel-security-advisor-of-donald-trump-who-may-get-position-in-fbi-or-cia%2Farticleshow%2F111599260.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-kash-patel-security-advisor-of-donald-trump-who-may-get-position-in-fbi-or-cia%2Famp_articleshow%2F111599260.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-kash-patel-security-advisor-of-donald-trump-who-may-get-position-in-fbi-or-cia%2Famp_articleshow%2F111599260.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Slashes%20Road%20Tax%20On%20Strong%20Hybrid%2C%20Plug-in%20Hybrid%20Electric%20Cars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20move%20towards%20promoting%20eco-friendly%20transportation%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20has%20announced%20a%20waiver%20of%20road%20tax%20on%20hybrid%20cars.%20This%20policy%20aims%20to%20encourage%20the%20adoption%20of%20greener%20vehicles%20and%20reduce%20the%20environmental%20impact%20of%20traditional%20gasoline%20and%20diesel-powered%20cars.%20Leading%20automakers%20Maruti%20Suzuki%20and%20Toyota%20are%20expected%20to%20benefit%20significantly%20from%20this%20decision.%20The%20exact%20quantum%20of%20reduction%20in%20the%20taxes%20is%20not%20revealed%20in%20the%20notification.%20However%2C%20reports%20have%20that%20a%20100%20per%20cent%20rebate%20is%20being%20offered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaruti%20Suzuki%2C%20with%20its%20popular%20hybrid%20models%20like%20the%20Grand%20Vitara%2C%20and%20Toyota%2C%20known%20for%20its%20efficient%20hybrid%20technology%20in%20models%20such%20as%20the%20Innova%20Hycross%20and%20Urban%20Cruiser%20Hyryder%2C%20stand%20to%20see%20increased%20sales%20and%20customer%20interest.%20The%20tax%20waiver%20reduces%20the%20overall%20cost%20of%20ownership%20for%20consumers%2C%20making%20hybrid%20vehicles%20a%20more%20attractive%20option%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20registration%20cost%20for%20the%20hybrid%20trims%20of%20the%20Grand%20Vitara%20and%20Urban%20Cruiser%20Hyryder%20is%20close%20to%20Rs%201.80%20lakh%20in%20UP.%20Thus%2C%20a%20significant%20cut%20in%20the%20on-road%20prices%20of%20these%20SUVs%20will%20be%20observed.%20The%20Innova%20Hycross%20and%20Invicto%20buyers%20will%20benefit%20with%20a%20cut%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20the%20on-road%20prices%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20variant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20this%20is%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20state's%20existing%20EV%20policy%2C%20the%20relaxation%20in%20registration%20cost%20will%20be%20valid%20till%20October%202025.%20Also%2C%20the%20overall%20demand%20for%20hybrid%20vehicles%20isn't%20very%20high%20across%20the%20country.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20government%20will%20not%20have%20to%20allocate%20a%20large%20budget%20to%20subsidise%20the%20registration%20of%20strong%20hybrid%20vehicles%20and%20PHEVs%20in%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKunal%20Behl%2C%20Vice%20President%2C%20Marketing%20%26amp%3B%20Sales%2C%20Honda%20Cars%20India%20Ltd%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWaving%20off%20100%25%20road%20tax%20on%20strong%20hybrid%20vehicles%20is%20a%20milestone%20decision%20by%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20which%20will%20encourage%20adoption%20of%20these%20environment%20friendly%20vehicles.%20%C2%A0%20At%20Honda%20Cars%20India%2C%20we%20welcome%20this%20move%2C%20as%20it%20will%20undoubtedly%20attract%20a%20larger%20set%20of%20customers%20to%20join%20the%20nation's%20green%20mobility%20mission.%20This%20forward-thinking%20decision%20will%20revolutionize%20the%20adoption%20of%20sustainable%20transportation%20in%20the%20state.%20Customers%20can%20now%20opt%20for%20eco-friendly%20hybrid%20vehicles%20like%20our%20City%20e%3AHEV%20in%20more%20affordable%20manner.%20This%20is%20also%20aligned%20with%20our%20global%20commitment%20to%20sustainable%20mobility%20and%20our%20global%20vision%20of%20achieving%20zero%20carbon%20emissions%20by%202050.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20aligns%20with%20the%20state's%20broader%20efforts%20to%20combat%20pollution%20and%20promote%20sustainable%20transportation%20solutions.%20By%20making%20hybrid%20vehicles%20more%20affordable%2C%20the%20UP%20government%20hopes%20to%20see%20a%20substantial%20rise%20in%20their%20adoption%2C%20contributing%20to%20cleaner%20air%20and%20a%20healthier%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20waiver%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20stimulate%20the%20automotive%20market%2C%20providing%20a%20boost%20to%20the%20hybrid%20car%20segment%20and%20encouraging%20other%20manufacturers%20to%20introduce%20more%20eco-friendly%20models.%20This%20progressive%20step%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20journey%20towards%20a%20greener%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20could%20soon%20be%20followed%20by%20other%20states%2C%20thereby%20giving%20a%20strong%20push%20to%20hybrid%20vehicles%2C%20which%20are%20often%20considered%20the%20sustainable%20substitute%20for%20ICE%20and%20battery-electric%20vehicles.%20Furthermore%2C%20it%20will%20push%20other%20carmakers%20to%20join%20the%20hybrid%20bandwagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720508700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ff9i67u78_maruti-suzuki-grand-vitara_625x300_09_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fauto%2Fup-govt-reduces-road-tax-strong-hybrid-cars-phev-grand-vitara-hyryder-innova-hycross-invicto-6065541%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20waives%20road%20tax%20on%20hybrid%20cars%20to%20promote%20eco-friendly%20transportation%2C%20benefiting%20models%20like%20the%20Maruti%20Suzuki%20Grand%20Vitara%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fauto%2Fup-govt-reduces-road-tax-strong-hybrid-cars-phev-grand-vitara-hyryder-innov