%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20were%20the%20words%20hurled%20at%20Shanaz%20Parveen%20when%20she%20first%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F182817%2Fmumbai-girl-taekwondo-olympics-national-champion-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraining%20for%20Taekwondo.%3C%2Fa%3E%20However%2C%20all%20these%20statements%20were%20mere%20white%20noise%20to%20young%20Shanaz%2C%20who%20remained%20focused%20on%20her%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20she%20is%20the%20first%20woman%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F190354%2Fladakh-marathon-chewang-motup-khardungla-challenge-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20Ladakh%20to%20win%20gold%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20a%20national-level%20Taekwondo%20meet!%20%E2%80%9CI%20kick%2C%20I%20knock%20off%20my%20opponent%20with%20my%20%3Cem%3Ehijab%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon!%E2%80%9D%20she%20proudly%20says.%20It%20was%20a%20school%20taekwondo%20session%20that%20sparked%20Shanaz%E2%80%99s%20interest%20in%20the%20sport.%20There%20was%20no%20looking%20back%20for%20her%20since.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20trained%20for%2010%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20and%20won%20several%20awards%20both%20national%20and%20international%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20faced%20constant%20pressure%20from%20her%20relatives%20and%20saw%20her%20friends%20quit%2C%20it%20was%20Shanaz%E2%80%99s%20mother%20who%20became%20her%20backbone.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20moved%20with%20me%20to%20Kargil%20for%20my%20training.%20We%20braved%20the%20tough%20weather%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20limited%20financial%20resources%20to%20be%20where%20I%20am%20today%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20from%20Ladakh%20to%20represent%20India%20at%20the%20World%20University%20Games%20in%20China.%20Additionally%2C%20as%20a%20black%20belt%20in%20Taekwondo%2C%20she%20als