0says%20Meghana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720016654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmeru-daycare-1720005938.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meghana%20Gorukanti%20Jupally%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Meru%20International%20School%20has%20launched%20a%20daycare%20centre%20called%20Meru%20Aveksha%2C%20which%20helps%20integrate%20kids%20of%20migrant%20workers%20into%20mainstream%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F355387%2Fmeru-international-school-tellapur-hyderabad-migrant-workers-children-daycare-learning-centre%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Back%20To%20My%20Childhood%E2%80%99%3A%20Kerala%20Man%20Turned%20a%20Barren%20Mining%20Site%20Into%20a%20Forest%20With%20Mud%20Homestays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Mustafa%20P%20A%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20which%20is%20not%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20cup%20of%20tea.%20He%20purchased%20a%20barren%20land%20which%20was%20once%20a%20mining%20site%20to%20transform%20it%20into%20a%20green%20oasis%20with%20trees%2C%20tropical%20forests%20and%20water%20bodies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20businessman%20by%20profession%2C%20it%20was%20his%20work%20trips%20to%20countries%20like%20China%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20Thailand%20that%20contributed%20to%20his%20inspiration%20to%20make%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F251997%2Fbengaluru-engineer-terrace-gardening-urban-jungle-organic-food-compost-green-hero-him16%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20private%20jungle.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20looked%20for%20the%20perfect%20land%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20before%20finding%20this%20one.%20His%20vision%20is%20a%20lush%20green%20tropical%20forest%20today.%20The%20Greenara%20Homestay%20is%20a%20part%20of%20that%20vision%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haneena%20P%20A%2C%20his%20daughter%20who%20manages%20the%20homestay%20with%20him%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20amidst%20the%20tropical%20forest%20that%20Mustafa%20planted%20in%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Karipur%2C%20surrounding%20it%20with%20seven%20water%20bodies%2C%20the%20homestay%20is%20the%20natural%20getaway%20of%20your%20dreams.%20The%20property%20with%20three%20stay%20options%20is%20made%20with%20natural%20materials%20like%20mud%2C%20straw%20and%20wood%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289271%2Fkerala-couple-build-zero-cement-eco-friendly-home-with-recycled-material-around-natural-rocks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20zero%20cement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20journey%20back%20to%20his%20childhood%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20Mustafa%20always%20missed%20living%20in%20the%20lush%2C%20green%20area.%20The%20inspiration%20behind%20the%20project%20was%20partly%20because%20he%20wanted%20to%20relive%20his%20childhood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20development%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Kerala%2C%20he%20felt%20like%20the%20green%20cover%20was%20reducing%20massively.%20In%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20his%20part%20in%20bringing%20it%20back%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20undertake%20the%20project.%20It%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20alerted%20him%20of%20the%20land%20where%20Greenara%20now%20stands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mustafa%20PA%2C%20founder%20of%20Greenara%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FUntitled-design-2024-07-02T193056.233-1719928906-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355236%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMustafa%20P%20A%2C%20founder%20of%20Greenara%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20visited%20the%20land%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20there%20was%20not%20even%20a%20single%20tree%20on%20the%20property.%20Mining%20had%20taken%20away%20the%20life%20of%20the%20place%20but%20I%20could%20envision%20a%20greener%20future%20for%20the%20place.%20While%20I%20visited%20the%20place%20in%20summer%2C%20I%20could%20see%20the%20presence%20of%20water%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20the%20process%20of%20building%20an%20ecosystem%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20spend%20a%20year%20studying.%20He%20referred%20to%20various%20books%20and%20videos%20and%20spoke%20to%20people%20who%20had%20taken%20up%20such%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20by%20creating%20a%20huge%20pond%20and%20then%20divided%20it%20into%20streams%20throughout%20the%20property.%20This%20water%20became%20the%20main%20source%20of%20water%20for%20life%20to%20flourish%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C