%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efreshwater%20pearl%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20keep%20watching%20television%20programmes%20where%20I%20was%20introduced%20to%20new%20types%20of%20farming%20like%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming.%20I%20found%20it%20interesting%20as%20one%20could%20earn%20handsomely%20by%20selling%20pearls.%20But%20it%20was%20risky%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20risk%20of%20taking%20up%20pearl%20farming%2C%20Gaurav%20feared%20breaking%20the%20idea%20to%20his%20family.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20shared%20the%20idea%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20they%20were%20not%20convinced%20at%20all.%20My%20family%20had%20been%20growing%20traditional%20crops%20like%20wheat%2C%20millet%2C%20and%20mustard.%20But%20I%20had%20never%20stepped%20out%20to%20watch%20what%20happened%20on%20our%20fields.%20I%20preferred%20staying%20in%20the%20comforts%20of%20air%20conditioners!%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gaurav%20ventured%20into%20freshwater%20pearl%20farming%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20do%20something%20unique.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpearl-farming-1-1719841061-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355089%5C%22